description: Manage Azure Event Hubs Authorizationrule connection strings for Geo Recovery configuration Alias.

commands.name: az eventhubs georecovery-alias authorization-rule keys list
commands.summary: Gets the primary and secondary connection strings for the Namespace.
commands.syntax:
az eventhubs georecovery-alias authorization-rule keys list --alias
                                                            --authorization-rule-name
                                                            --namespace-name
                                                            --resource-group
